name: Brasilio
description:
This Monument Charnelhouse is part of the collection of the municipal cemetery of san francisco in Curitiba/Brazil.

Monument Charnel house is architectural model, they has a complex materiality, the sacred space being secondary, it presents greater authorial possibility, the form presupposes the function,
have large proportions and gives notoriety to the tomb, having mostly eclectic references.
